      "Mr. Ravi Seneviratne, a retired Senior Deputy Inspector General of Police, holds a Master\u2019s Degree in Human Rights from the University of Colombo. He has served as a founding member of the Special Task Force (STF), former Deputy Director of the State Intelligence Service (SIS), First Secretary of the Sri Lanka Embassy in Thailand, and the Head of Sri Lanka Interpol Sri Lanka."
